high_descs: go to the sink
pick up the purple rag from the sink
take the rag to the toilet
put the rag on the back of the toilet
go to the bath tub basin
pick up the rag from the tub that is closest to you
take the rag to the toilet
lean the rag against the toilet paper on the back of the toilet
anns.task_desc: put two purple rags on the back of the toilet

high_descs: Turn left, turn right at the tub and walk to the sink.
Pick up the rag from the sink.
Turn right and look up at the back of the toilet.
Put the rag down on the back of the toilet.
Walk over to the tub.
Pick up the rag closest to the bar of soap.
Walk back over to the toilet.
Put the rag down on the back of the toilet, to the right of the first rag.
anns.task_desc: To move two rags to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the tub, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the purple rag out of the sink.
Turn right to face the toilet.
Put the purple rag on the left side of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the tub.
Pick up the rightmost purple rag out of the tub.
Turn right and walk over to the sink, then turn right and walk up to the toilet.
Put the purple rag to the right of the other purple rag on the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two purple rags to the toilet tank.
